    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1193344842">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1193344842" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1193344842" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1193344842">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/135294244/">ericlvyang</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">史学研究的《九阴真经》。读者应感谢作者近乎絮叨的文风，如今恐怕再无人肯这样，将毕生心法倾囊相授于一切有志于学者。其他学科研究者若参读此书，想必也可触类旁通，获益良多。作者其才似海，冀望一生能完成三部历史地理巨著。惜乎天不假年，未竟全功。得之傅孟真，失之傅孟真，冥冥天意，亦复何言！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1191040990">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1191040990" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1191040990" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1191040990">有用</a>
